<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your Event is Coming Up Soon!</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #f39c12;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }

      .event-details {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .map-container {
        margin: 20px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .checklist {
        background-color: #e8f4f8;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .weather {
        background-color: #f0f8ff;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888888;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #3498db;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .social-links {
        margin: 20px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .social-links a {
        margin: 0 10px;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Your Event is Tomorrow!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>
          We're excited to remind you that <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong> is
          happening tomorrow! Here's everything you need to know to make the
          most of your experience.
        </p>

        <div class="event-details">
          <h2>Event Details</h2>
          <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{eventDate}}</p>
          <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{eventLocation}}</p>
          <p><strong>Address:</strong> {{eventAddress}}</p>

        <div class="map-container">
          <a href="{{mapLink}}">
            <img
              src="{{mapImageUrl}}"
              alt="Map to {{eventLocation}}"
              style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border: 1px solid #ddd"
            />
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="weather">
          <h3>Weather Forecast</h3>
          <p>
            <img
              src="{{weatherIconUrl}}"
              alt="Weather"
              style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 10px"
            />{{weatherForecast}}
          </p>
          <p><em>{{weatherTip}}</em></p>
        </div>

        <h3>Quick Links</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="{{ticketLink}}">View/Download Your Ticket</a></li>
          <li><a href="{{eventDetailsLink}}">Full Event Information</a></li>
          <li><a href="{{faqLink}}">Frequently Asked Questions</a></li>         

        <p>
          If you can no longer attend, please
          <a href="{{cancellationLink}}">let us know</a> as soon as possible so
          we can offer your spot to someone on the waitlist.
        </p>

        <div class="social-links">
          <p>Connect with us and other attendees:</p>
          <a href="{{facebookEventLink}}">Facebook</a> |
          <a href="{{twitterHashtagLink}}">Twitter</a> |
          <a href="{{instagramLink}}">Instagram</a>
        </div>

        <p>We look forward to seeing you!</p>

        <p>
          Best regards,<br />
          The Scheduleflow Team
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          This email was sent to {{email}} regarding your registration for
          {{eventTitle}}.
        </p>
        <p>Â© {{currentYear}} Scheduleflow. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
          <a href="{{privacyPolicyLink}}">Privacy Policy</a> |
          <a href="{{termsOfServiceLink}}">Terms of Service</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
